    "description": {
      "value": "<h2><span style=\"font-family:Signika\">Let There Be Light</span></h2><p>The Keton are a custom Homebrew clan created by Artemys and Mr. Hey.</p><p>Members of the Keton clan have the unique Plasma Release. A powerful combination of Fire and Lightning that grants both devastating power and bright shows of power, but also the ability to create light.</p><hr /><h3><span style=\"font-family:Signika\">Keton Traits</span></h3><p><strong>Recommended Ability Score Increase</strong>: +2 Con, +1 Cha</p><p><strong>Speed</strong>: Your base walking speed is 30 feet.</p><p><strong>Skill Proficiencies</strong>: Performance, Chakra Control</p><p><strong>Plasma Release Affinity</strong>: You begin with either Fire or Lightning Release Affinity. (Pick One)</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
